<topic id="how-to-mysql">
  <title>Configuring a MySQL Database Connection</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Configure MySQL database connection</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>To configure the support for a MySQL database, follow this procedure:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-mysql-datasource.dita#configure-mysql-datasource">Configure
          MySQL <term>Data Source</term> drivers</xref>.</li>
      <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-mysql-connection.dita#configure-mysql-connection">Configure
          a MySQL <term>Connection</term>.</xref></li>
      <li>To view your connection, go to the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view <ph
          conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view-parenthesis"/> or switch to the
          <uicontrol>Database Perspective</uicontrol> (available from <menucascade>
          <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
        </menucascade>).</li>
    </ol>
  </body>
